content: I think I need to clarify the fact that we did take a 10-day vacation to Hawaii last December, and it was a family trip. We spent a lot of time planning it, and it was an amazing experience for all of us. I'm trying to plan this trip to Maui with a similar mindset, so I can make sure to set aside enough money for everything. Do you have any specific tips on how to save money on activities and attractions in Maui?
